    <string name="how_it_works_content">• Long press on the map to add a point (edit dialog opens automatically)\n• Short tap on a marker to view its details\n• Long press on a marker to delete it\n• Configure point properties: name and active time window (hour:minute)\n• Enable background tracking to monitor your location\n• When you enter a point\'s zone during its active time window:\n  - Fairtiq launches automatically\n  - The phone vibrates (3-burst pattern)\n  - The screen wakes up if locked\n• You must exit the zone and re-enter to trigger again (anti-spam)</string>
    
